<function>

access:   public

name: alnum

param: mixed, $value

param: bool, $blank, false

return: bool

</function>

Validate that a value is only letters (upper or lower case) and digits.

* Parameters:

 * mixed //$value//: The value to validate.

 * bool //$blank//: Allow blank values to be valid.

* Returns bool: True if valid, false if not.